- if current_user and current_user.provider? and current_user.id == @provider.id
  .row.row-fullscreen#provider-view-notice
    %h4.f300.centered-text.text-white
      Hi there,
      = (current_user.provider_name || current_user.first_name) + '!'
    %h5.f300.centered-text
      This is what your provider profile currently looks like to the public.
      %br
      If you would like to make changes, go to your
      = link_to 'account settings', account_path
      %br
      %br
      If you would like to share your page, please use this url:
      %br
      %span.wrapword
        = link_to (ENV['website_url'] + '/p/' + current_user.slug), provider_path(current_user.slug)

.row.row-fullscreen#provider-header
  .col-md-7.col-md-offset-5.darker-blue-bcg{ style: 'border-radius: 30px 0 0 30px; margin-top:50px; padding:25px; background-color: #387FCF; background-color: rgba(56, 127, 207, 0.7)' }
    %h1.centered-text.text-white Wake up to a better future
  .col-md-7.col-md-offset-5.darker-blue-bcg{ style: 'border-radius: 30px 0 0 30px; margin-top:20px; padding:25px; background-color: #387FCF; background-color: rgba(56, 127, 207, 0.7)' }
    %h3.text-light9.f600.spaced Let's work together to find a cure for sleep apnea
    %h4.text-light7
      Join my network of care providers, researchers, and people with sleep
      apnea to work together and help us improve treament outcomes, etc.
  .col-md-7.col-md-offset-5{ style: 'margin-top:70px' }
    .col-sm-4.col-xs-7.pull-right
    .col-sm-4.col-xs-7.pull-right
      = image_tag "myapnea/welcome/img-small/pcornet_logo_3x1.png", class: "partners-img img-responsive", id: "partner-PCORnet"
    .col-sm-4.col-xs-7.pull-right
      = image_tag "myapnea/welcome/img-small/bwh-logo_3x1.png", class: "partners-img img-responsive", id: "partner-BWH"

.row.row-fullscreen#provider-banner{style: 'margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px;'}
  - if @provider.photo.present?
    .col-lg-2.col-lg-offset-1.col-md-3.col-md-offset-1.col-xs-4
      = image_tag user_photo_url(@provider), alt: '', class: 'team-member-picture-md', style: 'float: right;'
    .col-lg-8.col-md-7.col-xs-7{ style: 'padding-left:20px;' }
      %h4.text-dark7
        = @provider.welcome_message
      %h4.primary-orange
        = '- ' + @provider.provider_name
  - else
    .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1{ style: 'padding-left:20px;' }
      %h4.text-dark7.centered-text
        = @provider.welcome_message
      %h4.primary-orange.centered-text
        = '-' + @provider.provider_name
  .col-lg-1{ style: 'background-color: white;' }
.row.row-fullscreen#community-tracker-provider
  .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1
    %h2.lighterer-blue.centered-text{ style: 'margin-top:5px;' }
      Current Community:
      %span.primary-blue
        = number_with_delimiter User.current.count
      members
.row.row-fullscreen#slide-2p
  .col-md-6.col-md-offset-1
    %h1.primary-blue{style: 'margin-top:150px; '} Our Mission
    %h3{style: 'color:rgba(0,0,0,.7);' }
      The mission of MyApnea.Org is to improve the diagnosis and treatment of sleep apnea through the
      %span.lighter-blue active engagement
      of patients, families, researchers, and healthcare providers in a community that facilitates patient-centered research.
  .col-md-4
    = image_tag 'myapnea/welcome/img-small/team-hands-cropped.jpg', class: 'hidden-sm hidden-xs'
.row.row-fullscreen#slide-3
  .col-md-3.col-md-offset-1
    = image_tag 'myapnea/welcome/img-large/unsplash-dont-stand-there.jpg', class: 'hidden-sm hidden-xs'
  .col-md-6.col-md-offset-1
    %h1.primary-blue Our Goal
    %h3{style: 'color:rgba(0,0,0,.7)' }
      By offering this network to your patients, and engaging with them actively
      outside of the office, they begin to feel a uniquely incredible quality of
      care. This community easily shows people with sleep apnea the amount of
      support they have from an international group of researchers, care
      providers, and fellow patients.
.row.row-fullscreen#slide-4
  .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
    %h1.primary-blue.f500.centered-text Our Community
    %h3
      MyApnea.Org is a community built by people with sleep apnea, family
      members, providers, and researchers to share and learn from one another.
  .col-md-1
  = link_to forums_path, class: 'community-highlight-links ' do
    .col-md-3.col-md-offset-1.col-xs-12.col-button.community-highlight.centered-text#community-highlight-1
      %h3.text-white Active Forums
      %p.lead
        Discuss with others about living with sleep apnea and what is important
        to you. Share ideas on how to promote the website to others. The more
        members we have, the more we can learn from each other and contribute to
        future research.
  = link_to surveys_path, class: 'community-highlight-links' do
    .col-md-3.col-xs-12.col-button.community.highlight.centered-text#community-highlight-2
      %h3.text-white Research Surveys
      %p.lead
        Answer a series of questions about symptoms, treatment, and related
        health conditions. Your answers will help the sleep apnea community
        better understand the disorder and where future research efforts should
        be directed.
  = link_to research_topics_path, class: 'community-highlight-links' do
    .col-md-3.col-xs-12.col-button.community.highlight.centered-text#community-highlight-2
      %h3.text-white Impact Questions
      %p.lead
        Cast your vote on which research questions matter to you most. Providers
        and researchers will share what is known about the highest ranked topics
        and if data is lacking they will endorse the topic as an important
        direction for future research.
.row#partners-banner
  .col-sm-12.col-md-4.col-md-offset-2.col-lg-3.col-lg-offset-3
    = image_tag 'myapnea/welcome/img-small/pcornet_logo.jpg', class: "partners-img img-responsive", id: "partner-PCORnet"
  .col-sm-12.col-md-4.col-lg-3
    = image_tag 'myapnea/welcome/img-small/bwh_logo.jpg', class: "partners-img img-responsive", id: "partner-BWH"
/ Signup sheet
%a{:name=>'signup'}
- unless current_user
  = render 'users/signup_form', resource: User.new( provider_id: @provider.id )
- else
  #slide5.row.row-fullscreen
    .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1.col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2.panel.signup-form
      .panel-body#panel-sign-up
        - if current_user.provider? and current_user.id == @provider.id
          %h4.f300.centered-text.spaced
            This is where potential members will be able to register and list
            you as their care provider. You can share this page with your
            patients and community members by using the link below. If you have
            any questions about this process or would like any help, please feel
            free to
            %a{ href: "mailto:support@myapnea.org" } contact us.
          %h4.f300.centered-text.spaced
            %strong Your personal url:
            %br
            %span.lighter-blue.wrapword= link_to ENV['website_url'] + '/p/' + current_user.slug, ENV['website_url'] + '/p/'+ current_user.slug
        - elsif current_user.provider_id == @provider.id
          %h3.f300.centered-text
            Hi there,
            = current_user.first_name + '!'
            It looks like
            = @provider.provider_name
            is your provider.
          %h4.f300.centered-text
            If you want to get in touch with them, feel free to
            = link_to('send them an email', "mailto:#{@provider.email}")+"."
        - else
          %h3.f300.centered-text
            Hi there,
            = current_user.first_name + '!'
            It looks like
            = @provider.provider_name
            is not your provider.
          %h4.f300.centered-text
            Do you want to list them as your primary care provider?
          %div{ style: 'text-align:center' }
            = link_to "Yes, list #{@provider.provider_name} as my provider!", update_account_path(:user => { provider_id: @provider.id }), method: :patch, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-lg'
